CODE:
- Define an abstract base class (ABC) for image sources so all sources
  (Reddit, Wallhaven, NASA, etc.) share a common interface and filtering contract.
  The ABC should enforce:
    - fetch_urls(..., min_width: int = 0) -> Iterator[str] on all sources
    - A standard filtering hook so each source can apply min_width its own way
      (API param for Wallhaven, metadata check for Reddit, Pillow header for NASA)
  This prevents future sources from accidentally omitting size filtering.
